Package: mymcfda
Title: Independent Reimplementation of Mean and Covariance Estimation for Functional Snippets
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrea", "Bianco", email = "andrea.bianco00.ab@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An independent R implementation of simulation and estimation
    tools for mean, variance, and covariance analysis of functional snippet data.
    The package was developed after studying the methodology introduced in
    Lin and Wang (2022), "Mean and Covariance Estimation for Functional Snippets",
    and is intended for personal research, methodological understanding,
    and comparative evaluation against the original published approach.
    This package does not import, wrap, or reuse code from the authors' package;
    it is a standalone reimplementation developed from the article and related
    methodological analysis.
